          "raw_text": "1 cup buttermilk (1 cup milk with 1 tbsp lemon)"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "13d01c8a-4cd1-4505-9c6c-c07aa50b95cd",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1| Prepare beforehand: I wanted buttermilk to be infused with earl grey tea, so I made my own buttermilk. I first heated up milk until it is just boiling, then added in earl grey leaves to steep for 10 minutes. Then, I let it cool. I added 1 tbsp lemon juice to make buttermilk."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "4a03e7db-441d-45d2-8716-aa58d4d9f631",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2| Preheat oven to 350. Grease bundt pan and dust with flour."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "c1369ec9-5c5c-4916-bef6-d09419b9d92a",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3| Sift together flour, baking powder, baking soda, salt, ground up tea."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "9e7dd337-8a82-4b5e-a7fe-cc37306ab8cc",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "4| Cream together butter and sugar until pale and fluffy, about 5 minutes."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "306e4a9a-969d-4201-9129-61c754efb098",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "5| Add in extract and beat until well incorporated, about 1-2 minutes."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "8e887beb-e54b-40bb-9609-0f76e1385f1f",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "6| Add in eggs, one at a time, making sure it is well incorporated after each addition."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "12d9f663-f256-4ebe-8584-d610840c151e",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "7| Add 1/3 of the flour mixture and mix. Add in 1/2 of buttermilk and mix. Add in another 1/3 of flour. Add in remaining \u00bd of buttermilk. Then, add in the remaining amount of flour. After each addition, mix until just combined. Do not over mix."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "67d0ffb9-b1db-4e59-b0a3-0f84218425d7",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "8| Pour batter evenly into the pan. Lightly tap it against a surface to remove any air bubbles."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "1dc7c417-d583-4a66-b35b-fe5b4031d58f",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "9| Bake for one hour, until toothpick inserted comes out clean. Invert onto a wire rack and cool for another hour."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "6f9ce43a-d55f-4ab2-aa6d-8902c1d341b0",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "10| Drizzle glaze on completely cooled cake."
        },
